Mode.intel-ivybridge.label="Intel® "Ivy BrIDge" Generation"
Mode.intel-ivybridge.summary="Applies the baseline feature 设置 of Intel® "Ivy BrIDge" Generation processors to all 主机s 在 集群.\n\n主机s 使用 following processor 类型s will be permitted to enter the 集群:\nIntel® "Ivy BrIDge" Generation\nIntel® "Haswell" Generation\nIntel® "Broadwell" Generation\nIntel® "Skylake" Generation\nIntel® "Cascade Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Ice Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Sapphire RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Emerald RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Granite RapIDs" Generation\nFuture Intel® processors\n\nCompared 到 Intel® "Sandy BrIDge" Generation EVC mode, this EVC mode exposes 添加itional CPU features including RDRAND, ENFSTRG, FSGSBASE, SMEP, 和 F16C.\n\n注意： Some "Ivy BrIDge" microarchitecture processors do not provIDE the full "Ivy BrIDge" feature 设置. Such processors do not sup端口 this EVC mode; they will only be admitted 到 Intel® "Nehalem" Generation mode or below.\n\nFor more 信息, see Knowledge Base article 1003212."
Mode.intel-haswell.label="Intel® "Haswell" Generation"
Mode.intel-haswell.summary="Applies the baseline feature 设置 of Intel® "Haswell" Generation processors to all 主机s 在 集群.\n\n主机s 使用 following processor 类型s will be permitted to enter the 集群:\nIntel® "Haswell" Generation\nIntel® "Broadwell" Generation\nIntel® "Skylake" Generation\nIntel® "Cascade Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Ice Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Sapphire RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Emerald RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Granite RapIDs" Generation\nFuture Intel® processors\n\nCompared 到 Intel® "Ivy BrIDge" Generation EVC mode, this EVC mode exposes 添加itional CPU features including Advanced Vector Extensions 2, f已用 multiply-添加s, Transactional 同步hronization Extensions, 和 new bit manipulation instructions.\n\n注意： Some "Haswell" microarchitecture processors do not provIDE the full "Haswell" feature 设置. Such processors do not sup端口 this EVC mode; they will only be admitted 到 Intel® "Nehalem" Generation mode or below.\n\nFor more 信息, see Knowledge Base article 1003212."
Mode.intel-broadwell.label="Intel® "Broadwell" Generation"
Mode.intel-broadwell.summary="Applies the baseline feature 设置 of Intel® "Broadwell" Generation processors to all 主机s 在 集群.\n\n主机s 使用 following processor 类型s will be permitted to enter the 集群:\nIntel® "Broadwell" Generation\nIntel® "Skylake" Generation\nIntel® "Cascade Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Ice Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Sapphire RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Emerald RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Granite RapIDs" Generation\nFuture Intel® processors\n\nCompared 到 Intel® "Haswell" Generation EVC mode, this EVC mode exposes 添加itional CPU features including Transactional 同步hronization Extensions, Supervisor Mode Access Pr事件ion, Multi-Precision 添加-Carry Instruction Extensions, PREFETCHW 和 RDSEED.\n\n注意： Some "Broadwell" microarchitecture processors do not provIDE the full "Broadwell" feature 设置. Such processors do not sup端口 this EVC mode; they will only be admitted 到 Intel® "Haswell" Generation mode or below.\n\nFor more 信息, see Knowledge Base article 1003212."
Mode.intel-skylake.label="Intel® "Skylake" Generation"
Mode.intel-skylake.summary="Applies the baseline feature 设置 of Intel® "Skylake" Generation processors to all 主机s 在 集群.\n\n主机s 使用 following processor 类型s will be permitted to enter the 集群:\nIntel® "Skylake" Generation\nIntel® "Cascade Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Ice Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Sapphire RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Emerald RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Granite RapIDs" Generation\nFuture Intel® processors\n\nCompared 到 Intel® "Broadwell" Generation EVC mode, this EVC mode exposes 添加itional CPU features including Advanced Vector Extensions 512, Persistent 内存 Sup端口 Instructions, Protection 键 Rights, 保存 Processor Extended 状态s with Compaction, 和 保存 Processor Extended 状态s Supervisor.\n\n注意： Some "Skylake" microarchitecture processors do not provIDE the full "Skylake" feature 设置. Such processors do not sup端口 this EVC mode; they will only be admitted 到 Intel® "Broadwell" Generation mode or below.\n\nFor more 信息, see Knowledge Base article 1003212."
Mode.intel-cascadelake.label="Intel® "Cascade Lake" Generation"
Mode.intel-cascadelake.summary="Applies the baseline feature 设置 of Intel® "Cascade Lake" Generation processors to all 主机s 在 集群.\n\n主机s 使用 following processor 类型s will be permitted to enter the 集群:\nIntel® "Cascade Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Ice Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Sapphire RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Emerald RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Granite RapIDs" Generation\nFuture Intel® processors\n\nCompared 到 Intel® "Skylake" Generation EVC mode, this EVC mode exposes 添加itional CPU features including VNNI 和 XGETBV with ECX = 1.\n\n注意： Some "Cascade Lake" microarchitecture processors do not provIDE the full "Cascade Lake" feature 设置. Such processors do not sup端口 this EVC mode; they will only be admitted 到 Intel® "Skylake" Generation mode or below.\n\nFor more 信息, see Knowledge Base article 1003212."
Mode.intel-icelake.label="Intel® "Ice Lake" Generation"
Mode.intel-icelake.summary="Applies the baseline feature 设置 of Intel® "Ice Lake" Generation processors to all 主机s 在 集群.\n\n主机s 使用 following processor 类型s will be permitted to enter the 集群:\nIntel® "Ice Lake" Generation\nIntel® "Sapphire RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Emerald RapIDs" Generation\nIntel® "Granite RapIDs" Generation\nFuture Intel® processors\n\nCompared 到 Intel® "Cascade Lake" Generation EVC mode, this EVC mode exposes 添加itional CPU features including SHA extensions, Vectorized AES, 用户 Mode Instruction Pr事件ion, Read Processor ID, Fast Short REP MOV, WBNOINVD, Galois Field New Instructions, 和 AVX512 Integer F已用 Multiply 添加, Vectorized Bit Manipulation, 和 Bit Algorithms Instructions.\n\n注意： Some "Ice Lake" microarchitecture processors do not provIDE the full "Ice Lake" feature 设置. Such processors do not sup端口 this EVC mode; they will only be admitted 到 Intel® "Cascade Lake" Generation mode or below.\n\nFor more 信息, see Knowledge Base article 1003212."
Mode.intel-sapphirerapids.label="Intel® "Sapphire RapIDs" Generation"
