Mode.amd-rev-e-no3dnow.summary="Applies the baseline feature 设置 of AMD Opteron™ Generation 1 ("Rev. E") processors, with 3DNow!™ sup端口 已移除, to all 主机s 在 集群.\n\n主机s 使用 following processor 类型s will be permitted to enter the 集群:\nAMD Opteron™ Generation 1 ("Rev. E")\nAMD Opteron™ Generation 2 ("Rev. F")\nAMD Opteron™ Generation 3 ("Greyhound")\n\nFor more 信息, see Knowledge Base article 1003212."
