Mode.amd-greyhound-no3dnow.label="AMD Opteron™ Gen. 3 (no 3DNow!™)"
Mode.amd-greyhound-no3dnow.summary="Applies the baseline feature 设置 of AMD Opteron™ Generation 3 ("Greyhound") processors, with 3DNow!™ sup端口 已移除, to all 主机s 在 集群.\n\n主机s 使用 following processor 类型s will be permitted to enter the 集群:\nAMD Opteron™ Generation 3 ("Greyhound")\nAMD Opteron™ Generation 4 ("Bulldozer")\nAMD Opteron™ "Pile驱动程序" Generation\nAMD Opteron™ "Steamroller" Generation\nAMD "Zen" Generation\nAMD "Zen 2" Generation\nAMD "Zen 3" Generation\nAMD "Zen 4" Generation\nAMD "Zen 5" Generation\nFuture AMD processors\n\nCompared 到 AMD Opteron™ Generation 2 EVC mode, this EVC mode exposes 添加itional CPU features including SSE4A, MisAlignSSE, POP计数, 和 ABM (LZCNT).\n\nFor more 信息, see Knowledge Base article 1003212."
Mode.amd-greyhound.label="AMD Opteron™ Generation 3"
