Mode.amd-zen2.summary="Applies the baseline feature 设置 of AMD "Zen 2" Generation processors to all 主机s 在 集群.\n\n主机s 使用 following processor 类型s will be permitted to enter the 集群:\nAMD "Zen 2" Generation\nAMD "Zen 3" Generation\nAMD "Zen 4" Generation\nAMD "Zen 5" Generation\nFuture AMD processors\n\nCompared 到 AMD "Zen" Generation EVC mode, this EVC mode exposes 添加itional CPU features including CLWB, UMIP, RDPID, XGETBV with ECX = 1, WBNOINVD, 和 GMET.\n\nFor more 信息, see Knowledge Base article 1003212."
Mode.amd-zen3.label="AMD Zen 3 Generation"
