Mode.amd-zen4.label="AMD Zen 4 Generation"
Mode.amd-zen4.summary="Applies the baseline feature 设置 of AMD "Zen 4" Generation processors to all 主机s 在 集群.\n\n主机s 使用 following processor 类型s will be permitted to enter the 集群:\nAMD "Zen 4" Generation\nAMD "Zen 5" Generation\nFuture AMD processors\n\nCompared 到 AMD "Zen 3" Generation EVC mode, this EVC mode exposes 添加itional CPU features including Fast Short CMPSB 和 STOSB, Automatic IBRS, AVX512BF16, AVX512BITALG, AVX512BW, AVX512CD, AVX512DQ, AVX512F, AVX512IFMA, AVX512VBMI, AVX512VBMI2, AVX512VL, AVX512VNNI, AVX512VPOPCNTDQ, GFNI, IBRS, 和 Upper 添加ress Ignore.\n\nFor more 信息, see Knowledge Base article 1003212."
